  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053000/extras/b4fc1c3a77068ea382fb4c11fe049ef0.poster.avif?t=1564243186\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053000/extras/b4fc1c3a77068ea382fb4c11fe049ef0.webm?t=1564243186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053000/extras/b4fc1c3a77068ea382fb4c11fe049ef0.mp4?t=1564243186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The war has begun. You are the last pilot on your base. The horde of enemy planes is coming on your base.<br><strong>PLANES ATTACK</strong> - is shoot 'em up game in which you need to defend the sky against enemy invaders.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Global Leaderboard<br></li><li> Dynamic gameplay blended with peaceful soundtrack<br></li><li> Steam Achievements</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053000/extras/3e578af7b79c02db0eef6a38388712e8.poster.avif?t=1564243186\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053000/extras/3e578af7b79c02db0eef6a38388712e8.webm?t=1564243186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053000/extras/3e578af7b79c02db0eef6a38388712e8.mp4?t=1564243186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
